{"tid":2420256,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"分半鐘科學–缺氧對癌細胞的好處","createTime":"2021-02-23T22:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T15:26:27.000Z","uid":38861,"like":56,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"37b06a07b885c1e99811e5bf4e58e72ce6c79fff","tid":2420256,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T22:13:31.000Z","msg":"上兩集簡述了癌細胞缺氧的成因，以及缺氧導致癌細胞相對上更為依賴葡萄糖作新陳代謝用途。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JnWAL6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJnWAL6X.jpg&h=326e8cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三十秒科學&ndash;腫瘤的周遭環境<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gFPfPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gFPfPS</a><br />\n<br />\n三十秒科學&ndash;癌細胞嗜糖的原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2416199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2416199</a><br />\n<br />\n今集我們會講述缺氧對癌細胞自身發展的其中一道好處。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）當DNA出現異變的時候，細胞裡名為p53的蛋白質便會出手幫忙，號令細胞停止生長(Cell cycle arrest)，給予時間讓其他蛋白質幫忙協助修復DNA。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzU6SM1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzU6SM1.jpg&h=6c9bad28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若果細胞最後還是無法處理修復DNA的工作，p53便會指示細胞趨向死亡程序(Apoptosis)。<br />\n<br />\n腫瘤的出現，是無數DNA變異得出來的成果。因此在這方面來看，p53是防止癌細胞出現的好幫手，因為p53會確保細胞的DNA不會出現變異，或指令出現DNA變異的細胞消失。<br />\n<br />\n但是，有一點非常矛盾的是，大部份普通細胞的p53蛋白質表達率非常低，它能否防止癌細胞出現這一點使人存疑。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）事實上，非常諷刺的是，氧氣含量越低的話，P53蛋白質的表達率便會越高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvwdxM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvwdxM4.jpg&h=9463d5a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在缺氧的環境下，擁有p53的蛋白質的細胞便會自動進行死亡。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）重大的問題是，有部份缺氧的癌細胞會發展出變異版本的p53，失去原有的功能。<br />\n在缺氧施加的壓力下，擁有正常p53版本的細胞會一一死去，變相幫忙篩選出擁有變異版本p53的細胞，使它們逐漸成為大多數。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfsPQyN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfsPQyN.jpg&h=45abd2ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而這些擁有變異版本p53的細胞，修復DNA的能力會大幅度被削弱，因而加劇了DNA變異速度，促成腫瘤繼續長大。<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）圖中為腫瘤形成的其中一道概論，癌細胞自製的缺氧環境，變相提供了一道挑選擁有更強DNA變異能力細胞的環境。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4Y7CdR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4Y7CdR.jpg&h=f12ba68f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實中大部分的的癌細胞均擁有p53變異，而擁有p53變異的細胞更具抵抗化療藥物cis-platin的能力。<br />\n<br />\n除缺氧外，大陽的紫外光亦是促使p53變異的好幫手，不少皮膚癌細胞均出現至少一處的p53變異。<br />\n<br />\n那些不塗防曬便與陽光玩遊戲的人，一直是在玩命。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmxkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=99717098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmxkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=dd7531e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8538748/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F8538748%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmxkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=bac0a222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8538748/</a>"},{"pid":"33ef55e100c6c0ca510675fc80bfb0fdcd933039","tid":2420256,"uid":302951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:00:37.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59654e10df7dcb0544de3b6b11be50075cae2e76","tid":2420256,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39657e5691e794c3d73d9f4737e5c557d374c569","tid":2420256,"uid":324563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70adb292ae54537c40cb9e3ba1d1286f8ca6e7c5","tid":2420256,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:19:15.000Z","msg":"睇唔明<br />\n結論係咩?<br />\n缺氧可以: <br />\n加速癌細胞, or <br />\n殺死癌細胞?"},{"pid":"eb9eb538860bc8417b278916148c2b6d638d160c","tid":2420256,"uid":38861,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"70adb292ae54537c40cb9e3ba1d1286f8ca6e7c5","tid":2420256,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:19:15.000Z","msg":"睇唔明<br />\n結論係咩?<br />\n缺氧可以: <br />\n加速癌細胞, or <br />\n殺死癌細胞?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:31:48.000Z","msg":"缺氧會殺死擁有p53正常版本的癌細胞，而倖幸生還的細胞會發展出變異版本p53，令到癌細胞更有優勢成長。<br />\n<br />\n或者可以當缺氧就係蠱毒，最終會發展出生存能力最強的癌細胞。"},{"pid":"9a16361c13f3c1346cc9f19398e6313f1b9a3a3c","tid":2420256,"uid":13872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:36:45.000Z","msg":"所以日常要吸大啖d空氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670651033dbbaa05638f67260e78fb957111e234","tid":2420256,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb9eb538860bc8417b278916148c2b6d638d160c","tid":2420256,"uid":38861,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"70adb292ae54537c40cb9e